- **Rationale**: Better matches actual distribution (~215K unique keys per thread across 64 threads). Fibonacci hashing with proper load factor → fewer collisions
- **Impact**: 2-5% speedup from better load factors (~7-17 ms improvement)

#### 3. **Explicit Final Set Capacity** (Clarity)
